---
// AboutC.astro - Timeline/Story Design
---

<section class="py-20 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, var(--color-brown) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <!-- Main Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-title text-brown mb-8 leading-tight">
        ELLA SKIN & SPA WELLNESS
      </h1>
      <div class="w-32 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-brown to-transparent mx-auto"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Story Timeline -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-16">
      
      <!-- Story Section 1 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-light to-pink rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-title text-brown mb-6">Nuestra Misión</h3>
            <p class="text-xl font-sans text-black leading-relaxed">
              En ELLA SKIN & SPA WELLNESS, misión es guiarte hacia el bienestar integral y la belleza.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 order-1 lg:order-2 text-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-brown to-brown-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-6xl font-title text-brown-light opacity-30">01</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Story Section 2 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12">
        <div class="lg:w-1/2">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brown-light to-brown rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl text-white">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-title mb-6">Tecnología & Calidez</h3>
            <p class="text-xl font-sans leading-relaxed opacity-90">
              He creado un espacio donde la tecnología de vanguardia y la calidez humana se fusionan para ofrecerte una experiencia de spa única y personalizada.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 text-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink to-pink-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-6xl font-title text-pink-light opacity-30">02</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Story Section 3 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-pink-light rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl border border-pink/20">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-title text-brown mb-6">Equipo Especializado</h3>
            <p class="text-xl font-sans text-black leading-relaxed">
              Cuento con un equipo de especialistas apasionados que se dedican a salud y belleza, utilizando productos de alta calidad y técnicas avanzadas.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 order-1 lg:order-2 text-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-brown to-brown-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197m13.5-9a2.5 2.5 0 11-5 0 2.5 2.5 0 015 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-6xl font-title text-brown-light opacity-30">03</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Final Story Section -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brown via-brown-light to-pink rounded-3xl p-12 md:p-16 shadow-2xl text-white max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-title mb-8">Tu Bienestar es Nuestra Prioridad</h3>
          <p class="text-xl font-sans leading-relaxed opacity-90 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Descubre un lugar para desconectar y reconectar contigo mismo. En ELLA SKIN & SPA WELLNESS, bienestar es mi prioridad.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 